messages.content: Alright, I'll make sure I let you know the next time I'm in town. Enjoy the rest of your time off!

I actually have a dentist appointment in the morning, so that won't work. Some other time, I guess. Have a good time with your grandparents, and a safe flight back. And my number is 734-263-1911, just for future reference.
Alright so my grandparents are coming in for lunch on Thursday, so we could maybe do breakfast or coffee or something in the morning. If not no worries.
Haha no worries. I could maybe do an early lunch on Thursday, I need to check when my grandparents are coming in. Friday I'm flying out. I'll find out and get back to you. Merry Christmas!

Hey! Sorry, meant to talk to you on church Sunday - my godmother was approaching from the other direction so I got confused lol. If you want to meet up Thursday/Friday this week, or Wednesday/Thursday next week, we could get lunch or dinner and catch up. If not, no problem. Merry Christmas!
